OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FAndy Burnham will promise to be
OL,7,F"unashamedly Labour" when he
OL,8,Fofficially becomes the party's leader
OL,9,Fon Friday before taking over from Sir
OL,10,FKeir Starmer as prime minister next
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FHe will say in a speech that his
OL,14,Fgovernment will have the "courage to
OL,15,Ffix the big things that politics has
OL,16,Fneglected" and the "conviction to
OL,17,Fargue for our plans".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@TO]vD@ZOUxD@JO]xD@TOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
