PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor,
OL,7,Fwho returned to Westminster last month
OL,8,Fas Makerfield MP, will be confirmed as
OL,9,FLabour leader in a special conference
OL,10,Fand then enter No 10 on Monday.
OL,12,FBurnham will set out plans to focus on
OL,13,Feconomic renewal, more public control
OL,14,Fand reindustrialisation.
OL,16,FHe is expected to say Britain took "a
OL,17,Fseries of wrong turns in the 1980s"
OL,18,Fwhen "political power was centralised
OL,19,Fand economic power privatised".
OL,26,@xD@dOUyD@cO]zD@FOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
