OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FMaking the economy work for people
OL,7,Facross the UK will require "a new path
OL,8,Fto the one we've been on for the last
OL,9,F40 years", he is set to say.
OL,11,FHe will promise that the party under
OL,12,Fhis leadership will be "unashamedly
OL,13,FLabour in our priorities and in the
OL,14,Fdecisions we take, putting people and
OL,15,Fplaces at the heart of everything we
OL,16,Fdo".
OL,26,@oD@\OUqD@IO]tD@XOUxD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
