PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FHe will pledge to make the party more
OL,7,Funited under his leadership and pay
OL,8,Ftribute to his predecessor for
OL,9,Freturning Labour to government, while
OL,10,Fpraising the achievements his party
OL,11,Fhas made so far since 2024, including
OL,12,Fon workers' rights, the NHS and the
OL,13,Fpassing of the Hillsborough Law.
OL,15,FBurnham was the only candidate to get
OL,16,Fthe required support to replace
OL,17,FStarmer as party leader after his
OL,18,Fresignation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
