FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FHe was backed by 369 of the party's
OL,7,F403 MPs, far surpassing the 81 needed,
OL,8,Fand secured the support of eight of
OL,9,Fthe 11 unions affiliated with the
OL,10,Fparty.
OL,12,FBurnham steps into the job at a time
OL,13,Fwhen his party has trailed Reform UK
OL,14,Fin opinion polls for nearly 18 months,
OL,15,Fand Labour will be hoping his presence
OL,16,Fwill spark a bounce and turn around
OL,17,Fits fortunes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
