CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FStarmer has said he believes Labour
OL,7,Fcan win the next election under Andy
OL,8,FBurnham, and that he is "proud to hand
OL,9,Fover the party in good shape" to his
OL,10,Fsuccessor.
OL,12,FQuestions remain about how far the
OL,13,Fformer mayor's plans will differ from
OL,14,FStarmer's agenda.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
