FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FBurnham has spoken about how he wants
OL,7,Fto push powers to local leaders
OL,8,Foutside Westminster as part of his
OL,9,Fdevolution agenda and to create a "No
OL,10,F10 North" outpost of Downing Street
OL,11,Fbased in Manchester.
OL,13,FHe has said he will stick to Rachel
OL,14,FReeves' fiscal rules as well as
OL,15,Fmanifesto pledges not to raise income
OL,16,Ftax, VAT or national insurance, but
OL,17,Fdeclined to rule out a wealth tax in
OL,18,Fan interview this week.
OL,26,@qD@cOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
