FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784251084
OL,3,CBurnham to pledge to be 'unashamedly
OL,4,CLabour' in first speech as party leader
OL,6,FThe make-up of his top team in Cabinet
OL,7,Fhas also not been confirmed, with
OL,8,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband, Home
OL,9,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood and Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary Yvette Cooper all rumoured
OL,11,Fas potential picks for his chancellor.
OL,13,FHe has drafted in Matthew McGregor,
OL,14,Fwho has worked on elections in the UK
OL,15,Fand abroad and is currently chief
OL,16,Fexecutive of campaign group 38
OL,17,FDegrees, as his No 10 director of
OL,18,Fpolitical strategy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
